♪ Help me to believe

26:20.665 --> 26:22.537
♪ Oh, I just wanna believe

26:22.580 --> 26:24.451
♪ Can you hear me?
Can you see me? ♪

26:24.494 --> 26:25.758
♪ What's inside of me?

26:25.800 --> 26:27.498
♪ Oh, I just wanna believe

26:27.541 --> 26:28.847
♪ If my life
