26:28.891 --> 26:32.460
♪ Help me to believe

26:43.426 --> 26:48.171
♪ Well, everybody
wants to find the circle ♪

26:48.214 --> 26:52.872
♪ The line of truth
that has no end ♪

26:52.914 --> 26:55.265
♪ Because so many nights
I've spent ♪

26:55.308 --> 26:57.180
♪ With the feeling of empty...

26:57.223 --> 26:58.181
Hey!

26:58.224 --> 26:59.269
Oh, hi.

26:59.313 --> 27:00.792
Hi.

27:00.836 --> 27:02.445
Oh, you're here
with someone?

27:02.490 --> 27:04.317
No, I'm just here.

27:04.361 --> 27:07.146
I thought Xander
was going to show up.

27:07.190 --> 27:09.323
Oh, are you guys
going out?

27:09.365 --> 27:10.890
No, we're just friends.

27:10.932 --> 27:13.544
We used to go out,
but we broke up.

27:13.587 --> 27:14.675
How come?

27:14.720 --> 27:18.070
He stole my Barbie.

27:18.114 --> 27:20.028
Oh, we were five.

27:20.073 --> 27:22.249
Oh.

27:22.291 --> 27:24.643
I don't actually date
a whole lot... lately.

27:24.685 --> 27:26.122
Why not?

27:26.165 --> 27:29.385
Well, when I'm
with a boy I like,

27:29.430 --> 27:32.693
it's hard for me to say
anything cool or witty

27:32.738 --> 27:33.955
or at all.

27:34.000 --> 27:35.914
I-I can usually make
a few vowel sounds,

27:35.958 --> 27:38.134
and then I have to go away.

27:38.177 --> 27:39.440
It's not that bad.

27:39.482 --> 27:41.181
No, it is.

27:41.223 --> 27:42.922
I think boys are
more interested

27:42.964 --> 27:44.923
in a girl who can talk.

27:44.967 --> 27:47.012
You really haven't
been dating lately.

27:47.056 --> 27:49.798
It's probably
easy for you.

27:49.842 --> 27:52.278
Yeah, real easy.

27:52.322 --> 27:55.455
I mean, you
don't seem too shy.

27:55.499 --> 27:57.284
Well, my philosophy--

27:57.326 --> 27:58.720
do you want to hear
my philosophy?

27:58.763 --> 27:59.677
Yeah, I do.

27:59.721 --> 28:01.114
Life is short.

28:01.156 --> 28:03.159
Life is short.

28:03.202 --> 28:04.987
Not original,
I'll grant you, but it's true.

28:05.030 --> 28:06.858
You know, why waste time
being all shy

28:06.902 --> 28:08.076
and worrying
about some guy

28:08.121 --> 28:09.730
and if he's
going to laugh at you?

28:09.775 --> 28:13.125
Seize the moment 'cause
tomorrow you might be dead.

28:13.169 --> 28:15.780
Oh, that's nice.

28:19.132 --> 28:21.655
Um, I'll be back
in a minute.

28:21.700 --> 28:24.746
Oh, that's okay. You
don't have to come back.

28:24.789 --> 28:28.228
I'll be back
in a minute.

28:28.270 --> 28:30.838
Seize the moment.

28:33.624 --> 28:36.584
♪ I feel love with my friends

28:36.626 --> 28:38.846
♪ I feel love in my songs

28:38.891 --> 28:41.545
